ke":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T02:40:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n支國政治：<br />\n個個阿諛奉承，冇人敢言，點會有不殺言官既情況出現<br />\n<br />\n<strong>習近平</strong>，<strong>2012年</strong>起為中華人民共和國第五代最高領導人，現任<strong>中國共產黨中央委員會總書記</strong>、中華人民共和國主席、中央軍事委員會主席。<br />\n<br />\n自2007年起開始出任中共第十七、十八、十九屆中國共產黨中央政治局常務委員會委員。黨政軍大權集一身。<br />\n<br />\n至於政黨政治，就係<strong>一黨專政</strong>囉，個人凌駕黨，黨凌駕百姓。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n算啦 都係主席最大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<strong>北宋皇帝</strong>實權都無而家<strong>黨書記</strong>咁大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<strong>宋仁宗</strong>想升格一位<strong>妃嬪</strong>都比朝臣彈劾</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">皇帝有後宮佳麗三千<br />\n總書記身邊得彭麻麻</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.orangenews.hk/pic/0/10/11/97/10119785_343328.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.orangenews.hk%2Fpic%2F0%2F10%2F11%2F97%2F10119785_343328.jpg&h=e4aedf53&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://jessicahk-uat-resources.s3-ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/files/img_20151022_153455_1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fjessicahk-uat-resources.s3-ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com%2Ffiles%2Fimg_20151022_153455_1.jpg&h=e19d0fd3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1cbe270b3654fff3245dd48b647d4d5ed348b739","tid":881601,"uid":52658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T04:35:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8161246dff483f47d3c4a9edf2c847302e5f5469","tid":881601,"uid":67896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T04:39:39.000Z","msg":"香港先有資格去同北宋比<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n大陸只係匈奴吐蕃呢類蠻夷<br />\n日撚日騷擾北宋r和約金"},{"pid":"ccc4533309e7f56aecc8e6c7297917ddb3a548fc","tid":881601,"u