世 實施仁政<br />\n宋真宗任用賢良 聆聽民意<br />\n宋仁宗仁愛寬厚 重視經濟 教化百姓<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n中國有邊樣野及得上北宋<br />\n連1000年前既國家都不如<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T12:54:14.000Z","msg":"北宋是沙佗人，突厥一支"},{"pid":"49e2b9cb4dd3c35af4c6f585ccff519b631a76d4","tid":881601,"uid":34772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T13:00:04.000Z","msg":"lm fyp做北宋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94a80eb019f1a1d8beea60360bbacfcf2e930afc","tid":881601,"uid":49197,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e64226137392941589f902ca1e04aeb25b4a36d4","tid":881601,"uid":99962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8e26e6962010ab36db7075456b98f49fcdc64b21","tid":881601,"uid":28624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T09:34:40.000Z","msg":"宋朝係中央集權<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T12:53:27.000Z","msg":"最主要係將軍權由武人轉為文人掌握<br />\n<br />\n所以秦檜殺岳飛一例就係顯示文人係宋既地位係最超然<br />\n<br />\n後來演變成明朝文人同皇帝日日鬥氣，玩野，嘈交，呢種士大夫風骨就係由宋朝養成"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T13:02:52.000Z","msg":"好意思鬧明朝文人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 胡惟庸 方孝儒 于謙 海瑞 楊漣 楊慎 楊廷和咩下場? 錦衣衛 東廠 西廠 廷杖咩黎?另外仲有朱元璋濫殺功臣、崇禎不停換首輔同害忠臣,根本明朝皇帝水平遠不如宋朝D皇帝<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5593339bc88090613c8ac3da023b51f2a6dd6d4","tid":881601,"uid":52658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"49e2b9cb4dd3c35af4c6f585ccff519b631a76d4","tid":881601,"uid":34772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T13:00:04.000Z","msg":"lm fyp做北宋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />